<a id="signs" class="is-page-anchor"></a>
<section class="section is-medium px-0" id="section-signs">
    <div class="container is-text-centered is-max-tablet">
        <h2 class="title"><span>Signs</span> of a platform closing</h2>
        <p>There will come when a platform will show signs of coming to the end of its life. This section will showcase any platform that we think you should be aware of and the reasons why.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cols">
        <div class="left">
            <p>There are several things that have happened identically in other platforms that have closed. It is important to note that these signs are not a dead given, but 9/10 it ends the same way.</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Upgraded VIP tiers</li>
                <li>Special offers</li>
                <li>Temporarily disabling withdrawals</li>
                <li>Customer support suddenly not responding</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <div class="image">
                <img src="/assets/images/logos/canaan.png" alt="Canaan">
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h4>Reasons to be aware</h4>
                <p>It has been announced on 30th April 2024 that there are some special offers. These offers include seemingly generous, such as refer a friend and get a $15 bonus and deposit $136 and they will match it, doubling your money. I would advice taking the bulk of your investment out.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

